casebody.data:
Linda A. BIRDETTE, petitioner,
v.
USCB CORPORATION, et al. No. 12-9300. Supreme Court of the United States May 20, 2013.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the United States *2396Court of Appeals for the Eleventh Circuit dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
